These contain the source code for Chapter 8.

- DeadlockExample.java is the program shown in Figure 8.4. To run this program, enter

	javac DeadlockExample.java
	java DeadlockExample

- ClockApplet.java is the program shown in Figure 8.6. To run this program, enter

	javac ClockApplet.java
	appletviewer ClockApplet.html

You may also open the file ClockApplet.html from a browser window. 
Once the applet is running, you should see the messages "suspending threaad" and
"resuming thread" on the Java console when you minimize and restore the applet.
